        {
            "review_id": "227446305",
            "steam_id": "76561198074572959",
            "playtime_minutes": 993,
            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 1,
            "weighted_score": 0.523809552192688,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "**⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ | 10/10**\r\n\r\nAssetto Corsa Competizione is hands down the most realistic racing simulator I've ever played.\r\n\r\nThe driving physics are incredible. Every car feels different, tire temperatures matter, track conditions evolve, and you can genuinely feel when you're pushing the car beyond its limits. When you nail a lap, it feels earned. When you make a mistake, it's usually because you did something wrong—not because the game cheated you. The sound design is phenomenal, the force feedback is excellent, and the attention to detail is on another level. Whether you're battling through a wet race, managing tire wear during a stint, or fighting for tenths of a second in qualifying, ACC delivers an experience that feels as close to real GT racing as most of us will ever get. The learning curve is steep, but that's part of what makes it so rewarding. Every hour you put into the game makes you a better driver. If you're looking for an arcade racer, this isn't it. If you want a true racing simulator that rewards skill, patience, and consistency, ACC is absolutely worth it."
        },
        {
