            "review_text": "Genuinely a great sim racing game with balanced graphics and physics. GT racing enjoyers please give this a try. You won't regret it, even the DLC packs(especially GT4 & Nürburgring 24H ) are worth the price if you get it on discount cycle. The major flaw you will notice is some of the players in online public lobbies, where they will crash you at full speed in corners for no reason. But yeah, aside from this you will have a great experience. If any car you wanna try as a beginner go for Aston Martin V8 Vantage GT3(My personal favourite so far). \n"
