            "review_text": "A brilliant game with truly realistic car physics, the ability to experiment with weather conditions, and a wide selection of tracks. Personally, I love playing around with different types of GT3 cars, from mid-engined models like the Ferrari 296 GT3 to wild, traditional front-engined cars with massive engines like the Mercedes AMG GT3 Evo, and Assetto Corsa Competizione is perfect for that. I’d recommend it to everyone; it’s a great environment for working on your sim driving skills."
